1
00:00:06,720 --> 00:00:08,079
[PREVIOUSLY]
Three gods join forces.

2
00:00:08,560 --> 00:00:09,719
Quite the spectacle.

3
00:00:10,240 --> 00:00:11,319
Ceaseless rabid barking.

4
00:00:11,680 --> 00:00:12,680
Such noise.

5
00:00:13,640 --> 00:00:13,959
I shall use my Divinity

6
00:00:14,040 --> 00:00:14,639
I shall use my Divinity

7
00:00:14,880 --> 00:00:15,239
I shall use my Divinity

8
00:00:15,840 --> 00:00:16,840
and my Divine Power

9
00:00:17,360 --> 00:00:19,359
to forge your Sword of God.

10
00:00:20,480 --> 00:00:22,359
I will uphold the will to protect,

11
00:00:23,560 --> 00:00:24,999
carry your will,

12
00:00:26,080 --> 00:00:27,679
the will of two worlds,

13
00:00:28,800 --> 00:00:30,759
to defeat the God of Retribution.

14
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:33,959
You are worthy of seeing this sword.

15
00:00:47,040 --> 00:00:49,519
Before the universe was born,

16
00:00:49,720 --> 00:00:51,279
amidst the endless void,

17
00:00:51,480 --> 00:00:54,359
there were only two deities:
Creation and Retribution.

18
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:56,959
But unlike Creation, who opened the world

19
00:00:56,960 --> 00:00:59,119
and birthed all living beings,

20
00:01:00,160 --> 00:01:00,919
Retribution

21
00:01:01,360 --> 00:01:03,239
was born hating the light,

22
00:01:03,720 --> 00:01:06,199
hating all life in existence.

23
00:01:07,200 --> 00:01:08,279
Its very birth

24
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:10,919
represented the antithesis of Creation:

25
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:13,399
the destruction of the cosmos.

26
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:17,399
Just as Creation bestowed infinite possibilities,

27
00:01:17,880 --> 00:01:20,039
Retribution would bring upon the world

28
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:22,719
its inevitable end.

29
00:01:24,040 --> 00:01:26,679
Unable to bear witness to the world's demise,

30
00:01:26,960 --> 00:01:28,599
Creation, at the moment of dissipation,

31
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:30,879
personally sealed Retribution away.

32
00:01:36,480 --> 00:01:39,199
But eroded by endless time,

33
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:41,639
even a seal cast by Creation

34
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:44,799
inevitably developed a hairline

35
00:01:45,080 --> 00:01:46,080
fracture.

36
00:01:47,840 --> 00:01:49,119
In that instant,

37
00:01:49,520 --> 00:01:51,439
Retribution did not hesitate to unleash

38
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:52,480
all of its power—

39
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:55,079
even sacrificing the majority of its essence—

40
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:57,479
successfully sending a wisp of its power

41
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:59,279
outside the seal.

42
00:01:59,960 --> 00:02:03,279
Thus, the prelude to destruction began.

43
00:02:04,240 --> 00:02:05,999
The first world this wisp descended upon

44
00:02:06,040 --> 00:02:08,319
was the

45
00:02:08,640 --> 00:02:09,640
Ancient Land.

46
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:11,399
The Ancient Land.

47
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:15,839
Retribution transformed into a new life form,

48
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:18,799
utilizing the growth properties of living beings

49
00:02:19,040 --> 00:02:20,679
to gradually dissolve the seal

50
00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:22,359
and reclaim its power.

51
00:02:24,320 --> 00:02:28,439
This life possessed a brand-new, nascent soul.

52
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:31,279
But for Retribution,

53
00:02:31,880 --> 00:02:34,519
it was merely a vessel, a tool.

54
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:39,399
Retribution lurked deep within its soul.

55
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,799
As it evolved,

56
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,599
it would seize control of the body

57
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:46,279
and destroy the Ancient Land.

58
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:51,919
But it underestimated

59
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,000
it underestimated

60
00:02:53,680 --> 00:02:55,399
the will of living beings.

61
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:58,879
All the powerhouses of the Ancient Land

62
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:00,799
offered their own blood as sacrifice,

63
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:03,519
forming the Ten-Earths Nine-Heavens
God-Slaying Array

64
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:05,199
to trap Retribution.

65
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:16,640
Ultimately,

66
00:03:17,080 --> 00:03:19,559
Retribution detonated all its power,

67
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:21,319
perishing alongside

68
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:23,359
the Ancient Land.

69
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:26,239
After Retribution's death,

70
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:28,679
the destructive energy that dissipated

71
00:03:28,800 --> 00:03:31,879
was partially absorbed by the
God-Slaying Array,

72
00:03:32,240 --> 00:03:34,879
but the remainder reincarnated once more.

73
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:37,559
It became the Nine-Headed Chimera.

74
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:40,919
It possessed nine chances at rebirth.

75
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:43,359
It intended to grow again,

76
00:03:45,280 --> 00:03:46,759
but it hadn't anticipated

77
00:03:47,640 --> 00:03:50,799
that in this dimension of darkness and fire,

78
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:53,279
vengeful spirits

79
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:55,959
were awaiting its return.

80
00:03:57,320 --> 00:03:58,879
That nascent life

81
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:01,919
experienced repeated, ignorant rebirths,

82
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,959
only to be slain by the spirits.

83
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,879
It did not know what crimes it had committed,

84
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:09,359
nor even its own name.

85
00:04:11,760 --> 00:04:12,760
Until,

86
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:15,119
during its final reincarnation,

87
00:04:15,760 --> 00:04:17,359
the battered creature

88
00:04:17,520 --> 00:04:20,239
was summoned by a ray of hope

89
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:21,519
to another world.

90
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:31,519
There, it encountered a small human.

91
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:33,519
For the first time,

92
00:04:34,120 --> 00:04:36,159
it was given a name of its own.

93
00:04:37,520 --> 00:04:38,119
No...

94
00:04:38,120 --> 00:04:38,639
And Retribution,

95
00:04:38,640 --> 00:04:39,239
and Retribution

96
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:39,879
remained hidden deep within its soul,

97
00:04:39,920 --> 00:04:42,319
lurking silently in the depths.

98
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,639
Using this human,

99
00:04:44,960 --> 00:04:46,519
it grew step by step,

100
00:04:47,360 --> 00:04:49,759
until it reclaimed enough power.

101
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:51,279
broke through the seal,

102
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,959
and once again became

103
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:56,559
the God of Retribution.

104
00:05:12,840 --> 00:05:14,239
Do you understand now, Brother?

105
00:05:14,600 --> 00:05:16,199
It is merely a vessel.

106
00:05:16,920 --> 00:05:18,199
Its body,

107
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:18,999
its power,

108
00:05:19,200 --> 00:05:20,639
even its soul,

109
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:22,919
all originate from me.

110
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,159
Without me,

111
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,199
it is nothing.

112
00:05:37,760 --> 00:05:40,039
How dare you bare your fangs at me?

113
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:47,640
Silence!

114
00:05:48,640 --> 00:05:49,799
You have no right to speak of Haoyue.

115
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,800
You have no right to utter his name.

116
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,439
Because of you,

117
00:05:53,000 --> 00:05:55,279
Haoyue was killed again and again,

118
00:05:55,720 --> 00:05:57,319
bearing the sins of destruction,

119
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,719
shouldering endless hatred in your stead.

120
00:06:00,920 --> 00:06:01,920
Yet you,

121
00:06:02,440 --> 00:06:04,479
could only hide within Haoyue's soul,

122
00:06:04,880 --> 00:06:07,079
a despicable, cowardly...

123
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:09,120
coward!

124
00:06:14,880 --> 00:06:16,519
Power of Destruction...

125
00:06:18,320 --> 00:06:18,719
Brother,

126
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:20,359
let's defeat him together.

127
00:06:22,080 --> 00:06:23,239
Together.

128
00:06:44,960 --> 00:06:46,199
Don't get it wrong.

129
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:48,319
Even if, by using this vessel,

130
00:06:48,640 --> 00:06:50,599
you possess a trace of destructive power,

131
00:06:51,280 --> 00:06:53,839
it is merely a fraction I discarded—

132
00:06:55,680 --> 00:06:56,839
a power that is one in a billion,

133
00:06:56,880 --> 00:06:57,999
a mere billionth of my strength.

134
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:05,760
Is that so?

135
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:07,639
The Power of Retribution

136
00:07:07,760 --> 00:07:08,999
is supreme.

137
00:07:09,440 --> 00:07:12,199
Even Creation could not erase it.

138
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:14,320
But now,

139
00:07:14,600 --> 00:07:17,279
Long Haochen has gathered the dual divinity

140
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:18,280
bestowed by the Demon God Emperor,

141
00:07:18,960 --> 00:07:21,119
and with Haoyue's assistance,

142
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:24,039
mastered a sliver of the origin of destruction.

143
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:26,319
All elemental attributes,

144
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,560
stripped away!

145
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:37,879
How dare you...

146
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:40,319
use my own power against me!

147
00:07:48,640 --> 00:07:49,679
It's not over yet.

148
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,159
Haoyue,

149
00:07:51,560 --> 00:07:52,279
Brother,

150
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:53,360
we are here.

151
00:07:59,920 --> 00:08:01,039
Shatter it!

152
00:08:01,560 --> 00:08:02,839
Long Haochen swings his sword
at Retribution.

153
00:08:02,960 --> 00:08:04,119
Long Haochen swings his sword
at Retribution.

154
00:08:04,320 --> 00:08:07,999
Becoming an unprecedented threat
to the Supreme God.

155
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:09,000
What?

156
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:11,199
Even if it's just a fraction of my power,

157
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,679
it is still the Power of Destruction.

158
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,160
It can wound me.

159
00:08:17,080 --> 00:08:18,799
How does it feel to be injured

160
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,240
by your own power?

161
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,159
Damn it.

162
00:08:22,720 --> 00:08:23,839
You actually possess

163
00:08:23,840 --> 00:08:25,079
power capable of hurting me.

164
00:08:25,920 --> 00:08:27,799
But do you truly understand destruction?

165
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:30,039
Watch closely.

166
00:08:30,920 --> 00:08:32,519
This is true destruction!

167
00:08:32,543 --> 00:08:54,343
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

168
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:56,239
Lowly vessel,

169
00:08:56,800 --> 00:08:58,719
I grant you one chance.

170
00:08:59,600 --> 00:09:01,639
Kneel, return my power,

171
00:09:02,040 --> 00:09:03,719
and merge with the great Retribution.

172
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:04,359
Become one with the great Retribution.

173
00:09:05,520 --> 00:09:07,279
Or I kill you

174
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:09,519
and take it myself.

175
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,359
We will never merge with you.

176
00:09:11,760 --> 00:09:12,479
That's right!

177
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,359
Not even in death!

178
00:09:13,560 --> 00:09:15,279
We will stay with Brother forever.

179
00:09:22,120 --> 00:09:23,839
Haoyue does not belong to you.

180
00:09:24,680 --> 00:09:25,680
He is...

181
00:09:26,200 --> 00:09:26,679
My younger brother.

182
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:27,680
My own brother.

183
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,719
Long Haochen,

184
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,959
I underestimated you.

185
00:09:32,280 --> 00:09:33,959
Since the birth of the universe,

186
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:37,479
you are the only existence
capable of threatening me.

187
00:09:38,400 --> 00:09:39,479
Therefore,

188
00:09:40,360 --> 00:09:42,039
I must kill you.

189
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:47,999
Now, the moment of Finality has arrived.

190
00:09:48,400 --> 00:09:50,039
Constellations fall silent,

191
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,719
mountain ranges crumble,

192
00:09:51,920 --> 00:09:53,479
all things cease to be.

193
00:09:55,920 --> 00:09:57,479
All destinies

194
00:09:58,280 --> 00:09:59,359
return to...

195
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:02,079
The Sword of World Annihilation!

196
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:08,799
Power of Creation!

197
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:09,840
Power of Creation!

198
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,239
The Power of Creation...

199
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:19,199
That bastard Creation

200
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,999
actually left this power for you.

201
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:23,199
Just to reach this step...

202
00:10:23,880 --> 00:10:25,839
We have already sacrificed too much.

203
00:10:26,520 --> 00:10:27,520
Grandfather,

204
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:28,959
Caier,

205
00:10:29,320 --> 00:10:30,320
Haoyue,

206
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,279
and everyone else.

207
00:10:32,800 --> 00:10:34,519
Everyone in this world.

208
00:10:36,240 --> 00:10:37,240
And I...

209
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:38,959
to protect humanity,

210
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:40,239
to protect my kin,

211
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,999
I will never let them down.

212
00:10:42,760 --> 00:10:43,839
At this moment,

213
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:46,439
the conviction Long Haochen possesses,

214
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:47,560
his power,

215
00:10:47,640 --> 00:10:50,039
and the hopes of this world for him,

216
00:10:50,400 --> 00:10:51,199
all converge here.

217
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,319
All gather at this point.

218
00:10:52,920 --> 00:10:56,759
Allowing him to unleash the most
pinnacle power he has ever known.

219
00:10:57,080 --> 00:10:58,639
And thus, he activates

220
00:10:59,080 --> 00:11:03,159
the ultimate form of the
Throne of Eternity and Creation.

221
00:11:04,160 --> 00:11:05,160
Divine Throne,

222
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:07,040
God Seat.

223
00:11:12,680 --> 00:11:13,959
Only in this way

224
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:18,199
can he truly harness that ultimate trump card

225
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:20,199
left for him by the God of Creation.

226
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,720
Long Haochen,

227
00:11:38,480 --> 00:11:40,799
this most pure Power of Creation...

228
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:42,959
You can use it

229
00:11:43,560 --> 00:11:46,399
to seal Retribution once more
for thousands of years.

230
00:11:47,520 --> 00:11:49,039
You, your loved ones,

231
00:11:49,520 --> 00:11:50,959
and your entire world,

232
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:54,679
can live out a happy and peaceful life.

233
00:11:55,680 --> 00:11:56,879
In a thousand years,

234
00:11:57,560 --> 00:11:59,119
perhaps someone else

235
00:11:59,120 --> 00:11:59,559
will take up this duty,

236
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:00,439
inherit this responsibility,

237
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,919
and tread the same path as you.

238
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:06,239
This is the best solution.

239
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,120
Seal it?

240
00:12:09,440 --> 00:12:11,079
You mean, in a thousand years,

241
00:12:11,520 --> 00:12:12,799
it will awaken again?

242
00:12:16,840 --> 00:12:17,439
No.

243
00:12:17,720 --> 00:12:19,359
I will not leave the catastrophe
of Retribution

244
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:20,839
for future generations.

245
00:12:21,520 --> 00:12:22,759
I will bring this

246
00:12:23,040 --> 00:12:24,519
to an end myself.

247
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:27,240
I have a method.

248
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:31,519
It's far too risky.

249
00:12:31,920 --> 00:12:33,719
Do you know what you'll be facing?

250
00:12:34,880 --> 00:12:35,880
I do.

251
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,439
But it's the only way.

252
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:43,239
Are you truly prepared to take this step?

253
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:53,480
Long Haochen,

254
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:55,879
what you are about to pay...

255
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:58,079
is an unimaginable,

256
00:12:58,400 --> 00:13:01,119
a price heavier than death itself.

257
00:13:01,840 --> 00:13:03,719
To answer your resolve,

258
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:06,439
the Throne will spare no expense,

259
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:07,399
granting you

260
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:09,359
its absolute, unreserved aid.

261
00:13:10,280 --> 00:13:12,239
May this burning heart of yours

262
00:13:14,960 --> 00:13:17,559
become the undying sun.

263
00:13:26,560 --> 00:13:29,559
This sword is the Sword of World Creation.

264
00:13:30,360 --> 00:13:32,279
With my twin eyes as sun and moon,

265
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:34,199
my spine as the mountains,

266
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:36,279
my breath transforming into wind and cloud,

267
00:13:36,720 --> 00:13:39,079
my blood surging into rivers and seas.

268
00:13:39,440 --> 00:13:40,839
All living beings

269
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,519
run wild and thrive.

270
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:48,319
All destinies

271
00:13:48,920 --> 00:13:50,039
begin with the King,

272
00:13:51,360 --> 00:13:52,959
the Sword of Creation!

273
00:13:58,880 --> 00:14:01,279
You think this can stop me?

274
00:14:10,360 --> 00:14:11,360
Destruction

275
00:14:11,800 --> 00:14:13,679
will inevitably descend.

276
00:14:28,920 --> 00:14:29,959
You have no chance.

277
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:42,079
What are you doing?

278
00:14:48,880 --> 00:14:49,880
Where is this?

279
00:14:50,640 --> 00:14:51,639
This is...

280
00:14:52,080 --> 00:14:53,959
the world I created.

281
00:14:54,680 --> 00:14:55,919
Long Haochen, have you gone mad?

282
00:14:56,280 --> 00:14:57,839
I thought you would exhaust
your power of creation

283
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:58,840
to seal me.

284
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:01,279
Yet you actually created a world?

285
00:15:01,720 --> 00:15:02,999
Have you forgotten

286
00:15:03,120 --> 00:15:05,319
that I was born to destroy worlds?

287
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:07,879
I will make you understand

288
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:10,599
what it means for creation
